    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for catching this, I believe the case you're ending up may be when you're having a widget that reads results (current refinements, or clear refinements probably in this case) in a root index without index name passed. The error is confusing so I've opened a PR to guard for that case and ensure that we can't have other cases of this behaviour",
